snippet.title: Holfraine - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/holfraine-ps4/

Holfraine is now available on PlayStation 4. 
Indie Hero Shooter. 3 VS 3. Play, shoot and have fun. 
Music by DimmyPlus. Authorised by Jamendo Licensing for Fluxart Studios. 
Holfraine is an indie videogame of the Hero Shooter genre. Battle with other players in the arena and be the best. Frenetic matches full of action and strategy.
Developed by Fluxart Studios with the support of PlayStation Talents.
